    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "I would suggest that you use Apache&#39;s commons logging utility. It is highly scalable and supports separate log files for different loggers. <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-logging/guide.html#Configuration\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">See here</a>."
